/**
 * Icon generation guide:
 * 
 * Required icons:
 * - icon.png: 1024x1024 (app icon)
 * - splash.png: 1242x2436 (splash screen)
 * - splash-ios.png: 1170x2532 (iPhone)
 * - splash-ios-tablet.png: 2048x2732 (iPad)
 * - splash-android.png: 1080x2220 (Android)
 * - adaptive-icon.png: 1080x1080 (Android adaptive icon)
 * - notification-icon.png: 96x96 (notification icon, white on transparent)
 * - favicon.png: 192x192 (web favicon)
 * 
 * Icons should be:
 * - PNG format with transparency where needed
 * - High quality (72 DPI minimum)
 * - Safe zone: Leave 10% margin on all sides for adaptive icons
 * - Branding colors: #667eea (primary), #f093fb (secondary)
 * 
 * Splash screen tips:
 * - Center your main content
 * - Use safe zone (avoid top/bottom 20%)
 * - Include app logo and name
 * - Use brand colors consistently
 * - Test on different device sizes
 */

/**
 * Asset generation command (if using expo-cli):
 * 
 * Generate icons from a single source image:
 * npx expo-cli@latest image-to-assets icon.png
 * npx expo-cli@latest image-to-assets splash.png --splash
 * 
 * Or manually:
 * 1. Create base image (1024x1024 minimum)
 * 2. Use online tools to generate different sizes
 * 3. Place files in assets/ directory
 */

